      <span class="warn"> <img src="[% c.request.base %]/static/images/bug.jpeg" ><br><br><br><br>" Hi [% c.user.name %], Jyo has modified the LIKE feature for you <br> ...... Just dial 999 if you find any bug ....... <br>"  </span>
